title: MHC.Voxynth.VSTi.v2.0-BEAT
description:
Description: Multimode Formant Filter - 20 different formant filters which vary between traditional A, E and O vocals to fictive formants, which sound unreal but still have a vocal character.
Performance keys - The lowest octave on your keyboard can be used to change the sound of the formant filter.
Polyphonic with 3 Oscillators Per Voice - 4 waveform shapes per oscillator.
Stereo Delay.
